.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, ritmeester, bolivar, bluemaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, tennis, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, bus, taxi
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
2. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person who's sport is surfing and the bolivar-smoker##2
5. the bolivar-smoker is not the person driving the taxi##6
6. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7
7. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | bolivar  | ritmeester  | alhambra |
| Sport   | snowboarding   | tennis | cycling | surfing     |
| Transport     | taxi    | bike     | boat     | bus         |

