3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the siglo-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the accountant is the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the engineer is the person driving the airplane##1
7. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
8. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the siglo-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | siglo    | swisher     | davidoff   | tiparillo      |
| Job   | project-manager    | engineer | accountant | coach  |
| Transport     | motorbike | airplane  | ship    | quad-bike |

