.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, sailing, ice-hockey
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, fuchsia, blue, black
4 different pets are kept: cat, horse, mouse, rabbit
1. the person who's sport is climbing is not the person who likes black##6
2. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the person who likes grey##7
3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who's sport is swimming##7
5. the person who's sport is swimming is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
8. the person who likes grey is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Sport      | swimming  | climbing | sailing | ice-hockey |
| Color   | black | blue  | fuchsia  | grey    |
| Pet           | rabbit | cat  | horse    | mouse    |

