3. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5
4. the engineer is somewhere between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsdahlia##7
5. the person who growsdaffodil is the teacher##1
6. the teacher is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
8. the engineer is not the british##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Job      | librarian     | engineer | teacher        | doctor       |
