3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the goat##2
4. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
7. the person who growstulip is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is golf##7
8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
9. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
