.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, disco, electronic, rock
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, scooter, snowmobile
1. the person drinking milk is not the person driving the scooter##6
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
3. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the boat is not the fan of disco##6
5. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the snowmobile##7
8. the person driving the scooter is not the fan of electronic##6
9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | r&b | rock  | electronic    |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | lemonade  | hot-chocolate | milk    |
| Transport     | jet-ski       | boat      | scooter    | snowmobile |

