7. the person drinking water is the mexican##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
9. the nigerian is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the bluemaster-smoker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster   | prince        | montecristo        | aristoff   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian   | indonesian | french |
| Beverage           | water  | juice | fanta       | mirinda |

