4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the car##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person driving the bus##7

.:: Answer ::.
